2.5.42.name: wordpress/pollme
2.5.42.description:
This plugin is only supported on PHP 5.2 or greater.

PollMe is an easy to use and easy to modify polling tool for WordPress. Written to be easy to use to none coders.

You can design as many polls as you wish , displaying the results as either a bar are pie chart using Google Charts you can also download the raw data into a spreadsheet.

If you are having trouble and cannot find the answers in the FAQ you can post your support questions to the WordPress Support Forum

If you find PollMe useful please rate it at wordpress.org and please consider making a donation to help us set aside more hours to maintain PollMe

PollMe is written by dcoda
